{"tid":2085414,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【疏忽照顧】水泡綁安全繩任由兒子獨游　6歲男童沉水底溺斃父母抱憾終生","createTime":"2020-06-30T01:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T03:36:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e9a45551d54a0bc891fb6ab86141cd69601d61fe","tid":2085414,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T01:17:07.000Z","msg":"近日天氣炎熱，不少人一家大細出動去海灘游泳消暑，不過家長要時刻留意小朋友安全，避免樂極生悲。內地有父母帶同6歲兒子去游泳，卻只在兒子的水泡綁安全繩，任由他獨自游泳，結果男童溺斃，父母難過得呼天搶地。<br />\n<br />\n據內地傳媒報道，事發於惠州，上周五（26日）一對父母帶著6歲的兒子，到東江沙公園嬉水。媽媽留在岸上，爸爸則為兒子戴上水泡，並繫上安全繩，父子二人一起游到離岸邊30多米的江中。<br />\n<br />\n男童脫離水泡安全繩<br />\n後來爸爸離開兒子身邊，並叫妻子在岸上留意著兒子，夫妻竟然就此讓兒子獨自在江中游泳。兒子其後脫離了水泡及安全繩，漸漸沉入4米深的水底。<br />\n<br />\n當男童的父母察覺異樣時已太遲，從在場人士拍攝到的影片可見，父母見江中只餘下兒子的水泡已心知不妙，在岸上的爸爸跪求泳客救子，並連聲呼叫「兒子呀」，在旁的媽媽則激動得大叫「求求你，快點救救他」。<br />\n<br />\n為時已晚父撫屍痛哭<br />\n事發後，到場的打撈隊及泳客均參與救援和打撈工作，最終找到男童。當時男童已沒有生命跡象，無論救護人員如何施救，都未能起死回生，爸爸只能撫屍痛哭。男童的遺體隨後被送至殯儀館處理。<br />\n<br />\n網民認為事件非常不幸，而男童的爸爸「嚴重失責」，父母因疏忽照顧，導致兒子喪命。有網民批評男童的父母，「才6歲的孩子，怎麼會允許在水裡離開自己的視力與活動範圍」。<br />\n<br />\n另外有網民建議父母帶小朋友玩水，要選擇安全水域，也不要離孩子太遠，必須控制距離，同時保留體力，以便孩子出現突發事故時可以立即救援。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2680000/2681944/swim_thumb_20200629_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2680000%2F2681944%2Fswim_thumb_20200629_ch_1024.jpg&h=b38c827d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88c2456f88dcddd45d43a5b69db894b421da3775","tid":2085414,"uid":204272,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T01:18:41.000Z","msg":"個老豆跪喊<br />\n但係唔落水救？<br />\n擺明特登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e019fae70f4259b312b47d1faec9c214bdbc85","tid":2085414,"uid":93479,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T01:19:22.000Z","msg":"呃保險下話"},{"pid":"df3bc575751ca44a80c64739ba7cbd2063320e5b","tid":2085414,"uid":93479,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T01:20:14.000Z","msg":"睇標題 &gt;估地方 (支那) &gt; 入去見到內地 &gt; 上一頁"},{"pid":"f9d0af590fe8e350ae6d9733aeddea45b4969753","tid":2085414,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T01:20:27.000Z","msg":"我唔get<br />\n正常人唔係就算無繩都會捉實救生圈架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b813a938701169c296066d35a2745a64758b16","tid":2085414,"uid":113922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T01:21:46.000Z","msg":"兒子其後脫離了水泡及安全繩<br />\n<br />\n抵啦，又係果d周街走既頑童"},{"pid":"873fc00c8fa9ebe0b7520d32f5e781c027820381","tid":2085414,"uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f9d0af590fe8e350ae6d9733aeddea45b4969753","tid":2085414,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T01:20:27.000Z","msg":"我唔get<br />\n正常人唔係就算無繩都會捉實救生圈架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:14:37.000Z","msg":"支那人唔係正常人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2927360ed31d081f73b16a552232dda75c2c9bfd","tid":2085414,"uid":115184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:17:15.000Z","msg":"祝下世投胎唔做支那人"},{"pid":"550d9832c2de47c3243123896ec3c3d8544b873a","tid":2085414,"uid":70771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:18:00.000Z","msg":"6歲就識重刷首抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/mouse.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da4f046c6dfe198de7027a6c846ba516e83b517","tid":2085414,"uid":59922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:18:20.000Z","msg":"係得支那人湊仔好似放狗咁放"},{"pid":"3067e27506212d03f6bf57adc2d59bd82bc3daba","tid":2085414,"uid":50801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:23:15.000Z","msg":"恭喜晒<br />\n只係捱左6年就可以重刷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c252dbeb816e8b18910b2663b711be4e1f2f35b","tid":2085414,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3440f7fe84ead9df2686fe6a03d94b97aafebba8","tid":2085414,"uid":292227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:31:15.000Z","msg":"買重哂燕疏啦，high到拍哂地<br />\n咁撚緊張個細路會4米深水唔九理佢？咪傻啦"},{"pid":"d5dddc4febf9ced829516edc99b7236cb271ef73","tid":2085414,"uid":161098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9d0af590fe8e350ae6d9733aeddea45b4969753","tid":2085414,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T01:20:27.000Z","msg":"我唔get<br />\n正常人唔係就算無繩都會捉實救生圈架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:31:26.000Z","msg":"啲𡃁仔on9起上嚟唔可以用常理諗<br />\n我細個都試過因為好奇 想甩咗個水泡睇下會點<br />\n甩到一半好彩我媽見到問我做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2a3af938137d4d9b5be0c8be80e52fde0d1683","tid":2085414,"uid":280746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:36:03.000Z","msg":"感謝黨<br />\n<br />\n你還有黨啊"}]}